  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your Queen Bee with unique skills and recruit an Artisan to build powerful turrets on the battlefield. Equip accessories, cast devastating spells, and defend your hive in this chaotic and personality-packed roguelike tower defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each run, explore maps filled with clever references, traps, and unique mechanics. Face unpredictable bosses and unlock magical cards of accessories and spells that can completely turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your resources, build strategic defenses, and experiment with millions of combinations to survive the endless Zombee swarms. <strong>Survive the Zumbeecalypse!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9cb255558a8a5d6ecb9e0aea9d450e79.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Choose your Queen, each with unique abilities <br>• Recruit Artisans with different towers and skills <br>• Build towers with distinct effects and functions <br>• Collect accessory and spell cards to create absurd synergies</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/91d385a13089d127473e08a1e24c1ff9.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/bcc41157ddebef8d4868bbc11f8470b2.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/bcc41157ddebef8d4868bbc11f8470b2.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/bcc41157ddebef8d4868bbc11f8470b2.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Face varied enemies with unpredictable behaviors <br>• Defeat bosses with unique mechanics and challenging phases <br>• Survive swarms, traps, and dynamic events</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/02ad17fc9036ea099aeedd44e1df5d3c.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9fb607212232a49983524fce8e0db1a4.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9fb607212232a49983524fce8e0db1a4.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9fb607212232a49983524fce8e0db1a4.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Explore regions overrun by chaos, with unique visuals and obstacles <br>• Discover references, secrets, and fun interactions around every corner <br>• Restore Meltopia and make the continent safe once again</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/640fd8368336106f442c6b58f32a4e1f.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9bb4c03eb2ab1701ca99f021ef5a832e.avif?t=1758895362\" width=301 height=163 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/4bbdcf89d946504eb713fc1934dace29.avif?t=1758895362\" width=301 height=163 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.webm?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9a5ab7a925f4ce35995f9e08dcbeba91.mp4?t=1758895362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your Queen Bee with unique skills and recruit an Artisan to build powerful turrets on the battlefield. Equip accessories, cast devastating spells, and defend your hive in this chaotic and personality-packed roguelike tower defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each run, explore maps filled with clever references, traps, and unique mechanics. Face unpredictable bosses and unlock magical cards of accessories and spells that can completely turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your resources, build strategic defenses, and experiment with millions of combinations to survive the endless Zombee swarms. <strong>Survive the Zumbeecalypse!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/9cb255558a8a5d6ecb9e0aea9d450e79.avif?t=1758895362\" width=620 height=88 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040270/extras/255a4d0c6b2b95c6fe86693c2d08b2d1.poster.avif?t=1758895362\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/304027